pedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the pair have won three world golds and two European golds as well as gold in Tokyo, 2024 has not been easy.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9994214751512294, \"rank\": 0.0005021675453641627, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Due to McCarthy being injured, the pair found themselves bumped down the seedings a little, with Italy and Switzerland ahead.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.6190794045335563, \"rank\": 0.6065613145589984, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6454706412925036, \"rank\": 0.5124177424103178, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.8553428119122011, \"rank\": 0.1588242853331273, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Little Davids again, that was a big, big upset\\\" - Paul O'Donovan will not be shaken in his belief that he and Fintan McCarthy are the underdogs after they won their men's lightweight semi-final#RTEsport#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/sPFewoSRzJ    And this has already proved to bean issue for O'Donovanwho raised it in an interview earlier this week.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul O'Donovan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He mentioned it again on Wednesday, as he doubled down on his 'David v Goliath' analogy.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He joked earlier in the week that the pair were \\\"the little Davids of this world going up against the Goliaths\\\" and this time around he said: \\\"Oh the little Davids again, that was a big, big upset, so it was.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Swiss are number two ranked, way above us, fastest time in the heat.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9954295463025408, \"rank\": 0.004347127355729629, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are happy to be able to put out that performance.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to IrishCentral's newsletter to stay up-to-date with everything Irish!\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All year we have been throwing the kitchen sink at them and just could not get ahead of them.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have had an answer to us every single time we haveraced this yearbut not today.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are hoping Friday we will be able to produce the goods again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McCarthy also mentioned that they'd set a record for the shortest amount of time they have ever spent on the water for a race.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.6190794045335563, \"rank\": 0.6065613145589984, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"* This article was originally published onExtra.ie.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related:Sports,TV & Streaming\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}]}"